Making R look prettier



To make R codes look better, you may want to install the fira font. Instruction can be found here and here.



# Without Fira code
x &lt;- 5  |&gt; 
    sqrt() |&gt; 
    round(2)


# With Fira code
x &lt;- 5  |&gt; 
    sqrt() |&gt; 
    round(2)

